    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont want to talk to a professional or anyone. that doesnt change the fact that my whole life is empty now. it just feels like i'm performing being okay for everyone. every morning i wake up and the weight of it is just too much. it feels like there's no point in even trying to fix it because the person who made it all make sense is gone. it just feels like a constant, heavy nothingness.",
